1623
01:35:30,976 --> 01:35:34,229
- I had an experience today, Pop.
- That so? What happened?

1624
01:35:34,312 --> 01:35:37,064
I wanted to tell you everything
from first to last.

1625
01:35:37,065 --> 01:35:39,942
It's been a strange day.
I had to wait quite a while.

1626
01:35:39,943 --> 01:35:41,402
- Oliver?
- Yeah, Oliver.

1627
01:35:41,403 --> 01:35:43,445
All day, as a matter of cold fact.

1628
01:35:43,446 --> 01:35:48,493
