but I was never a salesman for Oliver.

1632
01:35:58,378 --> 01:36:01,213
- What are you talking about?
- Hold onto the facts.

1633
01:36:01,214 --> 01:36:03,549
I was a shipping clerk.

1634
01:36:03,550 --> 01:36:05,592
- Listen to me...
- Dad, let me finish.

1635
01:36:05,593 --> 01:36:08,220
