about the past.

1636
01:36:08,221 --> 01:36:10,013
The woods are burning, boys.

1637
01:36:10,014 --> 01:36:12,725
There's a big blaze going on all around.

1638
01:36:12,726 --> 01:36:14,309
I was fired today.

1639
01:36:14,310 --> 01:36:16,061
How could you be?

1640
01:36:16,062 --> 01:36:20,275
