1647
01:36:39,210 --> 01:36:42,839
- What kind of welcome did he give you?
- He won't let you work on commission?

1648
01:36:42,922 --> 01:36:45,632
- I'm out! He gave you a warm welcome?
- Sure, Pop.

1649
01:36:45,633 --> 01:36:49,262
