of the amount.

1695
01:39:01,894 --> 01:39:05,523
- Then you... Then you got it?
- It's gonna be terrific, Pop.

1696
01:39:05,648 --> 01:39:08,066
Aw, then you got it, haven't you?

1697
01:39:08,067 --> 01:39:10,987
- You got it, haven't you? You got it!
- No.

1698
01:39:11,070 --> 01:39:13,655
I'm supposed to have lunch
with him tomorrow.

1699
01:39:13,656 --> 01:39:16,617
I'm telling you so you'll know
I can make an impression.

1700
01:39:16,701 --> 01:39:20,079
I'll make good somewheres,
but I can't go tomorrow.

1701
01:39:20,163 --> 01:39:22,289
- Why not? You simply...
