1702
01:39:22,290 --> 01:39:25,042
You give him the pen,
tell him it was an oversight.

1703
01:39:25,043 --> 01:39:26,585
- You have lunch.
- I can't.

1704
01:39:26,586 --> 01:39:29,337
You were doing a crossword puzzle,
you used his pen.

1705
01:39:29,338 --> 01:39:33,259
No, listen, kid,
I took those balls years ago, Pop,

1706
01:39:33,342 --> 01:39:36,387
and now I walk in with this fountain pen
